8. Hypaepeni, etc. The people of Hypaepa lived in Lydia on the southern slope of Tmolus. Tralles is in Caria on a tributary of the Maeander. The Laodicea here referred to was on the borders of Phrygia and Caria, on the river Lycus. Magnesia is probably the one on the Maeander.
